{% extends 'layout.twig' %} {% block title %} For Businesses {% endblock %} {% block content %}
<!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->
<div class="container marketing mt-5">
    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="display-3 text-center">Business is Good</h1>
                <p class="lead text-center">AlwaysOn is the new Wide Area WiFi Hotspot solution close to you in Koforidua - just the type you can afford. Available for the family or your business.</p>
                <p class="lead text-center">Same subscription, for the home, available to use throughout any of our WiFi zones.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <p class="text-center">
                <i class="fa fa-exchange fa-5x"></i>
            </p>
            <h2>Request Receiver</h2>
            <p>For a seamless network setup and maximum network throughput using the latest technologies at an affordable prices, we work with only Ubiquiti equipments. Thankfully, a receiver does not cost a fortune.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/support" role="button">Request Receiver</a></p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <p class="text-center">
                <i class="fa fa-wrench fa-5x"></i>
            </p>
            <h2>Quick Installations</h2>
            <p>The receiver can be mounted alongside your existing TV antenna on the same pole. We do the cabling and configurations same day, within a few hours, so you can get to your browsing quick!</p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <p class="text-center">
                <i class="fa fa-wifi fa-5x"></i>
            </p>
            <h2>Subscribe and Browse</h2>
            <p>Now the easiest part: Buy your AlwaysOn WiFi voucher from the nearest shop and start browsing. Or even better, buy via Mobile Money. The choice is yours</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/packages" role="button">Packages</a></p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.row -->
    <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="row my-0 mb-3">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Why AlwaysOn WiFi</h1>
            <p class="lead"><strong>For Businesses</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">All the For Home Benefits. <span class="text-muted">Plus even more.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Our business packages are built on top of the same benefits of having AlwaysOn WiFi for the home, except with even more goodness.</p>
            <p>Note: Businesses that go with the For Home packages will not enjoy the extra benefits that comes with For Business subscriptions. </p>
            <a href="/for-home" class="btn btn-outline-primary float-right">See the For Home Goodness</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="../public/assets/business1.jpg" alt="Significantly Affordable">
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Business-Oriented Packages. <span class="text-muted">Have all the enchilada</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Our understanding of the different types of internet users influences our choice of packages we offer. We have designed our packages to put little pressure on your use, however, allowing you to focus on doing more - in entertainment, education and research, and or video conferencing.
            </p>
            <p>A whole as a family, however each individual have internet preferences and usage levels. We cater for all with our flexible, reasonable packages. </p>
            <a href="/packages" class="btn btn-outline-primary float-left">Our Packages</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="../public/assets/business2.jpg" alt="Flexible Reasonable Packages">
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Business Network Support. <span class="text-muted">Everyday, Always.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">To ensure fast, reliable internet connections at all times, we depend on multiple network providers, thereby improving the consistency and response times. We do not put all our eggs in one basket. That means you get to stay online all the time, even if a network provider is facing challenges. </p>
            <p>In fact, you wouldn't know of any issues, as we allow you to Enjoy WiFi, Today.&trade;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="../public/assets/business3.jpg" alt="It's WiFi-ly Reliable">
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider" id="package">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-3">AlwaysOn WiFi Business Package</h2>
            <table class="table table-striped table-hover text-center">
                <thead class="thead-inverse">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Duration (Days)</th>
                        <th>Data Cap (Gig)</th>
                        <th>Price (Cedis)</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>30</td>
                        <td scope="row">Unlimited*</td>
                        <td>250</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>
              * Unlimited, as in, there is no data cap on usage per month, as long as usage falls within our <a href="/terms">Terms of Usage.</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-3">AlwaysOn WiFi for Businesses.</h2>
            <p>It costs less than Ghc 300 to get all the benefits of AlwaysOn WiFi for your business.
            </p>
            <p>Get in touch today. Let us all Enjoy WiFi, Today&trade;</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/support" role="button">AlwaysOn WiFi for your Business <i class="fa fa-building"></i></a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}